        make

    --no-warn-script-location \

FROM base

    apk add --no-cache \
        postgresql-libs geos proj-util

COPY backend backend/
COPY migrations migrations/
COPY scripts/world scripts/world/
COPY scripts/database scripts/database/
COPY manage.py .
